zig15 (0.15.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of zig15 package for danklinux
  * Binary repackaging of official Zig 0.15.2 release
  * For future Ghostty versions and other Zig projects
  * Installs to /usr/lib/zig-0.15.2 with /usr/bin/zig-0.15 symlink
  * Can coexist with zig14 and other Zig versions

